9.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "3. \"Government Irregularities, Tendency to Tyranny and Corruption\"", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-6", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "Third Essay. \"ON THE PRINCIPLE OF ASSOCIATION\"", "level": 3, "id": "ME11-39-7", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "Fourth Essay. \"ON THE PRINCIPLE OF AUTHORITY\"", "level": 3, "id": "ME11-39-8", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "1. \"The Traditional Negation of Government. Emergence of the Idea Which Succeeds It\" (p. 116)", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-9", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "2. \"General Critique of the Idea of Authority\" (p. 141)", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-10", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "Fifth Essay. \"SOCIAL LIQUIDATION\"", "level": 3, "id": "ME11-39-11", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "1. \"National Bank\"", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-12", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "2. \"The National Debt\"", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-13", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "3. \"Mortgage Debts, Simple Bonds\"", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-14", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "4. \"Buildings\"", "level": 4, "id": "ME11-39-15", "source_file": "MECW11-039.html", "chapter_number": 39, "filename": "MECW11-039.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "5. \"Landed P